Package SponsoredProject

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    SponsoredProject
    SponsoredProject class is the class that represents all the information about the sponsored Project, mainly: The date of the sponsored project The description of the sponsored project The target amount of the sponsored project The donated amount of the sponsored project
    SponsoredProjectDateComparator
    SponsoredProjectComparator enables the user to sort the sponsored projects based on their dates
    SponsoredProjectDonatedAmountComparator
    SponsoredProjectDonatedAmountComparator enables the user to sort the sponsored projects based on their donated amount
    SponsoredProjectList
    MessageList is the list that contains all the sponsored projects
    SponsoredProjectTargetAmountComparator
    SponsoredProjectTargetAmountComparator enables the user to sort the requests based on their sponsored project amount
